content.description: This proposal is proposing for upgrading the LikeCoin chain public testnet software from sheungwan to fotan.Details: - target software version:  fotan - version code: fotan-1   - repo: https://github.com/likecoin/likecoin-chain/tree/fotan-1   - Docker image: "likecoin/likecoin-chain:fotan-1-testnet"   - commit hash: 32056fc4759d276a11180256474cc4ed5e3ed8d4 - halt time: 2021-07-28T20:00:00+08:00 (in Unix timestamp: 1627473600) - parameters for genesis migration:   - iscn-registry-name: "likecoin-chain-testnet"   - iscn-fee-per-byte: "10000.000000000000000000nanoekil"   - chain-id: "likecoin-public-testnet-3"Right before the halt time, validators shall join into a realtime conference for preparing the upgrade and discussing issues during the upgrade.
content.title: Upgrade LikeCoin Chain testnet to Fotan
